import { Trans, useTranslation, withTranslation } from "react-i18next";
function headerComponent(props){
   const { t, i18n } = useTranslation();

   return (<thead className="header">
   <tr>
       <th onClick={() =>props.refreshWeathers("_id", this.state.weathers) }>{"cityId"}</th>
       <th onClick={() =>props.refreshWeathers("name", this.state.weathers) }>{ t('header.cityName')}</th>
       <th onClick={() =>props.refreshWeathers("coord.lat", this.state.weathers) }>{"latitude"}</th>
       <th onClick={() =>props.refreshWeathers("coord.lon", this.state.weathers) }>{"longitude"}</th>
       <th onClick={() =>props.refreshWeathers("sys.country", this.state.weathers) }>{"country"}</th>
       <th onClick={() =>props.refreshWeathers("weatherMain.humidity", this.state.weathers) }>{"humidity"}</th>
       <th onClick={() =>props.refreshWeathers("weatherMain.feels_like", this.state.weathers) }>{"feels like"}</th>
       <th onClick={() =>props.refreshWeathers("weatherMain.temp", this.state.weathers) }>{"temperature"}</th>
       <th onClick={() =>props.refreshWeathers("weatherMain.temp_max", this.state.weathers) }>{"maximum temperature"}</th>
       <th onClick={() =>props.refreshWeathers("weatherMain.temp_min", this.state.weathers) }>{"minimal temperature"}</th>
       <th onClick={() =>props.refreshWeathers("weather.description", this.state.weathers) }>{"description"}</th>                                
   </tr>
</thead>)

}
export default withTranslation()(headerComponent)
